  "texts": [
    "• Experience (15/42).",
    "If the author drew on past experience, participants tended to consider the text to have been written by a human.",
    "Arguments based on facts were considered more likely to be AI-generated.",
    "• Provision of justifications (12/42).",
    "There were several arguments that this feature was favored in AI-generated texts, with characteristics such as over-justifying by giving more information than necessary, or even providing definitions of terms, such that the reasoning failed to make sense."
